No. 540. Metropolitan Life Insurance Company, Petitioner, v. Camilla B. Talbott, Administratrix, etc. Jan*615uary 13, 1908. Mr. Maurice E. Locke for petitioner. Mr. Meriwether L. Crawford for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
